guy\u00ean Nh\u00edu m\u00e0y l\u1eafc \u0111\u1ea7u.\n    Ch\u1edb c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u l\u1eddi, m\u01b0a \u0111\u00e3 ng\u1eebng, c\u00e1c ng\u01b0\u01a1i v\u1eabn l\u00e0 tranh th\u1ee7 th\u1eddi gian xu\u1ed1ng n\u00fai \u0111i!\"\n    - \u0110\u00fang v\u1eady, D\u1ecbch huynh n\u00f3i r\u1ea5t \u0111\u00fang! - \u0110\u00fang \u0111\u00fang, xu\u1ed1ng n\u00fai xu\u1ed1ng n\u00fai!\n    Ba ng\u01b0\u1eddi ch\u1ed1ng \u0111\u1ee1 nhanh ch\u00f3ng \u0111\u1ee9ng d\u1eady, v\u1eeba \u0111i v\u1eeba v\u1ed7 b\u1ee5i b\u1eb7m c\u00f9ng c\u1ecf kh\u00f4 tr\u00ean ng\u01b0\u1eddi, m\u1ed9t kh\u1eafc c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n \u1edf \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e2u d\u00e0i.\n    Nh\u01b0ng ba ng\u01b0\u1eddi m\u1edbi \u0111i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c v\u00e0i b\u01b0\u1edbc li\u1ec1n l\u1eadp t\u1ee9c ph\u1ea3n \u1ee9ng l\u1ea1i c\u00e1i g\u00ec, quay \u0111\u1ea7u nh\u00ecn v\u1ec1 ph\u00eda D\u1ecbch Th\u01b0 Nguy\u00ean.\n    \"D\u1ecbch huynh? Ng\u01b0\u01a1i kh\u00f4ng \u0111i sao? \u201d\n    D\u1ecbch Th\u01b0 Nguy\u00ean c\u01b0\u1eddi l\u1eafc \u0111\u1ea7u.\n    \"Ta v\u1ed1n l\u00e0 c\u00f3 vi\u1ec7c v\u00e0o n\u00fai, h\u00e1 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u1eadp t\u1ee9c \u0111i, m\u1ea5y v\u1ecb m\u1eddi v\u1ec1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111i.\"\n    Ba ng\u01b0\u1eddi hai m\u1eb7t nh\u00ecn nhau, b\u1ed7ng nhi\u00ean c\u00f3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u00fd th\u1ee9c \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u00e1i g\u00ec, th\u00e2n th\u1ec3 m\u00e3nh li\u1ec7t gi\u1eadt m\u00ecnh, kh\u00f4ng d\u00e1m n\u00f3i th\u00eam g\u00ec n\u1eefa, hung h\u0103ng t\u00fam hai ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i, l\u00f4i k\u00e9o b\u1ecdn h\u1ecd v\u1ed9i v\u00e0ng r\u1eddi \u0111i.\n    -----------------\n    PS: Tu ti\u00ean s\u1ef1 t\u00ecnh xem nh\u01b0 k\u1ebf ti\u1ebfp m\u1edbi b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u.", "font_size": 14, "font_family": "Segoe UI"}, {"id": 4, "name": "EN", "data": "Chapter 26: Interesting Facts about the Tea Shed \n     Yi Shuyuan had doubts and surprises in his heart, but beyond this, his tension relaxed, wasn't this exactly the mysterious thing he was looking forward to?\n    Thinking so, Yi Shuyuan smiled slightly, took the initiative to walk to the table next to the old man, pulled out a stool and sat down.\n    The three people opened their mouths, and one of them said \"hey\", and they were pulled twice by their companions to stop making a sound, and stood there together looking at Yi Shuyuan worriedly.\n    And Yi Shuyuan shook his head with a smile and said in relief.\n    \"It's just a convenient tea house, old man, I want to taste this tea, I don't know if it's convenient?\"\n    \"What's the inconvenience!\"\n    The old man turned a cup from the tea set on the table, and then took the teapot to pour a cup of tea for Yi Shuyuan without hurry, the tea color was clear, the tea was fragrant and thick, just smelling it made people feel refreshed.\n    Yi Shuyuan was also not polite, picked up the teacup and blew lightly a few times, then took a sip, and suddenly a sweet warm current with a clear fragrance infiltrated the tip of the tongue, even if Yi Shuyuan in his two lives is not a fastidious person, he has never understood any tea ceremony, and he also thinks that this tea is very wonderful.\n    \"Good tea! Qingfeng Spring shallow cloud smoke road, Kuonan Mountain rain and fog slightly hazy, worthy of the name of pine fog, good tea! \u201d\n    Yi Shuyuan's improvisational work made the old man's eyes brighten, and he laughed heartily when he heard this.\n    \"Hahahahahaha, Gongzi is so talented, this remark makes the old man very gratified! Well, the three of you don't want to blow the wind by the eaves anymore, why not come and sit? \u201d\n    Yi Shuyuan also nodded slightly towards the three.\n    The three of them obviously hesitated, and after twisting for a while, they also walked over, and they all sat around Yi Shuyuan's table.\n    The old man poured tea for the three of them one by one, and several people saw that Yi Shuyuan had nothing to d