s not that he was thinking too much, but that the old man was talking about it!\n    After a while, Yi Shuyuan's heart was excited, funny and emotional.\n    \"So it is abhorrent to rob a doll's house, but that person may not have done it intentionally, oh, old man, if you can meet that doll, please tell me, I believe his house will go back soon.\"\n    The old man smiled and nodded and shook his head, but continued anyway.\n    \"Gongzi don't have to worry about it, although the doll is very pitiful when crying, but the house where the doll lived may not be the doll's, it was originally given by heaven and earth, and who followed it is also to see the sky, if a few people are here tonight for one night, right?\"\n    Yi Shuyuan also smiled, hearing this, of course he realized that the Huangshi that served as an inkstone was a treasure.\n    But Yi Shuyuan was not originally a greedy villain, after experiencing the overnight trial of wronged souls and seeing Lin Xiu's responsibility at that moment, he felt that people have something to do and not do, at least this treasure, he didn't plan to want.\n    It's not that Yi Shuyuan is worried about the retaliation of some mountain spirit, if he really has the ability to take revenge, why wait so long?\n    \"The old man said and smiled, I Yi Shuyuan is not a saint, but I will not rob a child's precious things, I borrowed some time before, and I will return it next time I bring it.\"\n    When the old man heard this, he stood up and saluted sincerely in the face of Yi Shuyuan.\n    \"Gongzi has an open heart, which makes the old immortal admire!\"\n    \"Don't dare to be, don't dare!\"\n    Yi Shuyuan hurriedly stood up and solemnly returned the salute, so that the three scholars who had just chatted with themselves and did not notice that they were a little confused, and they didn't know what happened between the two of them, obviously they were pulling a family.\n    -----------------\n    I don't know how long it took,